"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-lifestyle-team-mongolia-unveils-stunning-olympic-uniforms-for-paris-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbTeam Mongolia unveils stunning Olympic uniforms for Paris 2024  Mongolia's team has captivated the world with its stunning uniforms for the 2024 Paris Olympics designed by fashion brand Michel & Amazonka.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 183, \"end\": 191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999960855348, \"rank\": 3.914512428956905e-09, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}, {\"begin\": 230, \"end\": 240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999998708518, \"rank\": 1.2926331494005172e-10, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 242, \"end\": 250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999960855348, \"rank\": 3.914512428956905e-09, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a spectacular revelation, Mongolia has introduced what many are calling the most beautiful uniforms of the 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 413, \"end\": 421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999960855348, \"rank\": 3.914512428956905e-09, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Designed by the innovative Mongolian fashion brand Michel&Amazonka, these outfits have set the internet abuzz.\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 620, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 537, \"end\": 546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongols\", \"score\": 0.9571960627040806, \"rank\": 0.031913708678638644, \"text\": \"Mongolian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongols\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongols\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sisters Michel, Amazonka, and Munkhjargal Choigaalaa founded the label in 2015.\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 701, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is renowned for blending modern and traditional designs uniquely, according toDesign Taxi.\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 796, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The unveiling of the uniforms sparked widespread admiration online.\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 865, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is truly a blend of beauty and tradition,\\\" commented one enthusiastic netizen.\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 949, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another quipped, \\\"Winning a medal seems secondary as long as first impressions are top-notch!\\\"\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 1045, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The internet seems to agree, with many joking that Mongolia has already won the Olympics with their stunning attire.\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1098, \"end\": 1106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999960855348, \"rank\": 3.914512428956905e-09, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Michel&Amazonka uniforms are a masterpiece of cultural heritage and modern fashion.\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1252, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The female flag bearer's outfit includes a traditional robe dress, known as a feel.\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1337, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1265, \"end\": 1276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Standard-bearer\", \"score\": 0.9999999999035936, \"rank\": 7.495550872733275e-11, \"text\": \"flag bearer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Standard-bearer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Standard-bearer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The robe dress was paired with an embroidered vest, handbag, heels, and earrings.\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1420, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This ensemble beautifully marries traditional Mongolian motifs with a contemporary style.\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1468, \"end\": 1477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongols\", \"score\": 0.9571960627040806, \"rank\": 0.031913708678638644, \"text\": \"Mongolian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongols\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongols\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another female model showcased a similar embroidered vest, pleated skirt, blouse, and accessories.\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1611, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All represented the female team Mongolia athletes' uniform.\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1672, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1645, \"end\": 1653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999960855348, \"rank\": 3.914512428956905e-09, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The male flag bearer's uniform features a thin cotton robe adorned with traditional embroidery.\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1683, \"end\": 1694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Standard-bearer\", \"score\": 0.9999999999035936, \"rank\": 7.495550872733275e-11, \"text\": \"flag bearer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Standard-bearer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Standard-bearer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Mongolia, this embroidery is considered auspicious, according to theSouth China Morning Post.\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1867, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1774, \"end\": 1782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999960855348, \"rank\": 3.914512428956905e-09, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}, {\"begin\": 1848, \"end\": 1853, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9546279848609852, \"rank\": 0.0475283730192708, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1854, \"end\": 1861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Early_Show\", \"score\": 0.9999999960423338, \"rank\": 3.645401984342013e-09, \"text\": \"Morning\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Early_Show\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Early_Show\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They complete it with an embroidered vest, traditional boots, and an embellished belt.\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1955, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Male athletes will don a Mandarin collar shirt, pants, an embroidered vest, and sneakers.\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 2046, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fashion commentators have not held back their praise.\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2101, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A well-known fashion influencer, Ryan Yip expressed his awe on Instagram.\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2176, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2136, \"end\": 2144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Yip\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ryan Yip\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Yip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Yip\"}, {\"begin\": 2166, \"end\": 2175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1553184144776004e-36, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Tell me why we read about fashion every day, but I have never seen this until now.\\\"\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2262, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He added, \\\"These uniforms are not just runway pieces; they are couture uniforms for the Mongolian team.\\\"\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2352, \"end\": 2361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongols\", \"score\": 0.9571960627040806, \"rank\": 0.031913708678638644, \"text\": \"Mongolian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongols\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongols\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reactions from netizens have been overwhelmingly positive for Team Mongolia's uniforms.\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2457, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2385, \"end\": 2393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netizen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"netizens\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netizen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netizen\"}, {\"begin\": 2437, \"end\": 2445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999960855348, \"rank\": 3.914512428956905e-09, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One user commented, \\\"Who told the whole Mongolian Olympic team to pop off that hard?\\\"\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2544, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2499, \"end\": 2508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongols\", \"score\": 0.9571960627040806, \"rank\": 0.031913708678638644, \"text\": \"Mongolian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongols\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongols\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another remarked, \\\"They just won the Olympics before it even started.\\\"\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2616, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A netizen wrote, \\\"It's a reimagined version of our traditional attire, which I think best represents Mongolians.\\\"\", \"from\": 2618, \"to\": 2731, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2620, \"end\": 2627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netizen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"netizen\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netizen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netizen\"}, {\"begin\": 2719, \"end\": 2729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongols\", \"score\": 0.9896756941995687, \"rank\": 0.010432007998174914, \"text\": \"Mongolians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongols\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongols\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The internet's love for these uniforms is palpable.\", \"from\": 2733, \"to\": 2784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are comments like, \\\"Best uniforms ever,\\\" and, \\\"I gasped out loud when you said these are their Olympic uniforms,\\\" flooding social media.\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2928, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, not everyone agrees, according toToday.\", \"from\": 2930, \"to\": 2978, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some critics argue that Team Mongolia's designs, while beautiful, might not be practical for the summer heat in Paris.\", \"from\": 2980, \"to\": 3098, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3009, \"end\": 3017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999960855348, \"rank\": 3.914512428956905e-09, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}, {\"begin\": 3092, \"end\": 3097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6497852860966406e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One sceptic scoffed, \\\"I would not want to be caught sweating in that heat wearing that.\\\"\", \"from\": 3100, \"to\": 3188, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet, as the saying goes, beauty is pain, and it seems many are willing to overlook practicality for style.\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3296, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2024ParisOlympics will see athletes from over 200 countries competing in 329 events across 32 sports.\", \"from\": 3298, \"to\": 3403, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With such fierce competition, standing out is no easy feat.\", \"from\": 3404, \"to\": 3463, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But with Michel&Amazonka's exquisite designs, Team Mongolia has certainly made a memorable entrance.\", \"from\": 3465, \"to\": 3565, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3516, \"end\": 3524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999960855348, \"rank\": 3.914512428956905e-09, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the world anticipates the start of the Olympic Games on 26 July, all eyes will be on Team Mongolia's athletes.\", \"from\": 3567, \"to\": 3680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3660, \"end\": 3668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999960855348, \"rank\": 3.914512428956905e-09, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The attention will not just be for their performance but for their outstanding fashion statement.\", \"from\": 3682, \"to\": 3779, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a world where first impressions matter, Mongolia has undoubtedly made a grand one.\", \"from\": 3781, \"to\": 3866, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3824, \"end\": 3832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999960855348, \"rank\": 3.914512428956905e-09, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As one netizen aptly put it, \\\"They won before the Olympics even started.\\\"\", \"from\": 3868, \"to\": 3941, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With such high praise, Team Mongolia will dazzle both on and off the field.\", \"from\": 3943, \"to\": 4018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3971, \"end\": 3979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999999960855348, \"rank\": 3.914512428956905e-09, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What did you think of the uniforms?\", \"from\": 4019, \"to\": 4054, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know by clicking on the comment tab below this article or by emailinginfo@thesouthafrican.comor by sending a WhatsApp to 060 011 021 1.\", \"from\": 4056, \"to\": 4198, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4172, \"end\": 4180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9912926278883439, \"rank\": 0.008783856417911465, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can also follow@TheSAnews on XandThe South African on Facebookfor the latest news.\", \"from\": 4200, \"to\": 4286, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'The South African' is hiring!\", \"from\": 4288, \"to\": 4318, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Freelance writer positions available.\", \"from\": 4319, \"to\": 4356, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Send us your CV  While some fans are showing love and support to La Toya Jackson, some comments under her social media posts reflect worry for her health.\", \"from\": 4357, \"to\": 4511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4422, \"end\": 4437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Toya_Jackson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7062389355276127e-34, \"text\": \"La Toya Jackson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Toya_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Toya_Jackson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Somizi Mhlongo used his fame to teach a shopping mother to pay attention to her children while out in public.\", \"from\": 4513, \"to\": 4622, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4513, \"end\": 4527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Somizi_Mhlongo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Somizi Mhlongo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Somizi_Mhlongo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Somizi_Mhlongo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All eyes will be locked on the New Peter Mokaba Stadium as it serves as the backdrop for an epic conclusion to the Carling Knockout Cup.\", \"from\": 4624, \"to\": 4760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4659, \"end\": 4671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Mokaba\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Peter Mokaba\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Mokaba\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Mokaba\"}, {\"begin\": 4739, \"end\": 4746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carling_Brewery\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.30