nt.No agenda.No bias.\", \"from\": 5298, \"to\": 5335, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our offices are for administrative purposes only, no visitors will be accepted without an appointment.\", \"from\": 5337, \"to\": 5439, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"South Africa- Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd - Registration Number: 2005/028472/07 - Address: Regus Business Centre, 1st Floor, Block B, North Park, Black River Park, 2 Fir Street, Observatory, Cape Town, 7925, South Africa  Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 5441, \"to\": 5730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5579, \"end\": 5589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newcastle_Great_Park\", \"score\": 0.9981559113837044, \"rank\": 0.0018474955615399892, \"text\": \"North Park\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newcastle_Great_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newcastle_Great_Park\"}, {\"begin\": 5623, \"end\": 5645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Observatory,_Cape_Town\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Observatory, Cape Town\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Observatory,_Cape_Town\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Observatory,_Cape_Town\"}, {\"begin\": 5653, \"end\": 5665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5660180077194454e-16, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}]}"